. Volker Schürmann macht mit Hegel, Misch und Plessner die Weichenstellungen sichtbar, um dieses Entweder-oder in einer politischen Lesart von Unergründlichkeit unterlaufen zu können.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aBiopolitik. 4aDeutsche Philosophiegeschichte. 4aEntzauberung. 4aIntuition. 4aKulturphilosophie. 4aLebensphilosophie. 4aNaturphilosophie. 4aPhilosophie. 4aPlessner. 4aPraxis. 4aPraxisphilosophie. 4aUnmittelbarkeit. 7aPHILOSOPHY / History & Surveys / Modern.2bisacsh  aBiopolitics.  aGerman History of Philosophy.  aPhilosophy of Culture.  aPhilosophy of Nature.  aPhilosophy.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102523008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2010-2013z9783110352856oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Geschichte 2010-2013z97831103707370 cprintz978383761905840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839419052?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839419052423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839419052/original  a978-3-11-037073-7  transcript Highlight Collection Geschichte 2010-2013c2010d2013  a978-3-11-102523-0  transcript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TSOc2010d2013